name: Intercloud Throughput
shortDescription: Why are so few megabits per second flowing from one cloud region to another? Is it distance? Inter-cloud bottlenecks? Test throughput (and latency) between regions of GCP and/or AWS
longDescription: Why are so few megabits per second flowing from one cloud region to another? Is it distance? Inter-cloud bottlenecks? Test throughput (and latency) between regions of GCP and/or AWS
